{"tid":300742,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有無漫畫係寫實地講日本傳統？","createTime":"2017-06-28T06:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T09:22:20.000Z","uid":54785,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a10ee8be5424fcaf31e2a7767dfb2b8e100efdd","tid":300742,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:45:34.000Z","msg":"小弟去完京都之後，對日本傳統有好大興趣，想搵本漫畫黎睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然好多漫都有日本精神係入面，但想搵一套專講呢樣野既<br />\n<br />\n主題可以係茶道，禮儀，甚至劍道等等，但因為想睇關於內在d 既精神，所以唔太想睇打打殺殺果d 情節<br />\n<br />\n畫風方面我係鐘意醫龍 Jojo 果種<br />\n不過新版獵人 火撚我都接受到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有無推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60028504156716641bb8851cc14c837c6e75fa6","tid":300742,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"殺殺草紙 大江戶奇騷天外<br />\n殺殺草紙 大江戸無殘十三苦"},{"pid":"ca339e21c2e236ff0771955f21bca48279d98a43","tid":300742,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"夏目友人帳"},{"pid":"aeaccea6f210602d8c2b72fbeb1997c28e253139","tid":300742,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殺殺草紙 大江戶奇騷天外<br />\n殺殺草紙 大江戸無殘十三苦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝<br />\n系列漫黎？"},{"pid":"a475dcd9e0d63bc86eed6a74ae384648df5d358d","tid":300742,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夏目友人帳</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝"},{"pid":"77bd2516f7e574c3e571dc74f340e4bee9cc2b9f","tid":300742,"uid":41434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06