normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想係唔同既野上面睇到佢地背後既精神<br />\n<br />\n以前睇黎睇去都係食物，日式面包王果類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁可以睇下火之丸相撲，雖則係王道漫，不過對相撲有好多方面既闡述 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/154381\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/154381</a>"},{"pid":"995eeb7283af0044d47eab840c500c852ee23e1b","tid":300742,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T07:55:45.000Z","msg":"動畫都睇?怪化貓"},{"pid":"6e873f4cd032549f02b11b943692e5319b9d1785","tid":300742,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T08:02:36.000Z","msg":"黃金神威"},{"pid":"6bae829dca4002280a2ff50a4f863f47bef4ced7","tid":300742,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T08:42:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大唐雙龍傳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903c2d74a222c75789f7edb08b9d23155e6689ab","tid":300742,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T08:43:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>school days</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}